<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/23892014">参加「知乎盐 Club '13」是怎样一种体验？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1738576" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">相关问题：<br><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/23895326" class="internal">2014 年 5 月 24 日的「知乎盐 Club '13」活动有哪些亮点和槽点？</a><br><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/23912204" class="internal">没能参加「知乎盐 Club '13」是怎样一种体验？</a><br><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/23897520" class="internal">知乎盐club有哪些可以改进的点？</a></div>


</div>
